        </li>
        <li>
          <em
            class="text-secondary block not-italic md:text-base text-sm font-normal leading-normal pt-8"
            >
          </em>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>*/}
    <section class="pt-8">
      <SubHeading text="My Hobbies" />
      <em
        class="text-secondary block not-italic md:text-base text-sm font-normal leading-normal pt-8"
      >
       I highly value work-life balance, 
       I believe it's not only important for personal mental and physical wellbeing, 
       but also helps obtaining new perspectives on things and in turn contributes to better work results.
       I regularly exercise and do rock climbing (semi-professionnaly) and volleyball. 
       I enjoy artistic activities that stimulate my creativity like playing the piano, guitar and drawing, as well as watching movies.
      </em>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
